warehouse.ui

Class ProductTableModel

  • java.lang.Object
    • javax.swing.table.AbstractTableModel
      • warehouse.ui.ProductTableModel
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    Serializable, TableModel

    public class ProductTableModel
extends AbstractTableModel
    Provides a specific implementation for a AbstractTableModel that is used in the WarehouseManager. It defines the columns of a JTable and its types. If the data of the ProductTableModel is changed, the graphical representation in the corresponding table in WarehouseManager is changed as well.
    Author:
    OOP
